1
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:11,240
In terms of familiarity with Malaya

2
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,560
and Mr. Qin,

3
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,520
I am the most suitable person to go.

4
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:16,720
I want to fulfill Mingshu's dying wish.

5
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,200
Okay, okay, okay.

6
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:20,760
Even if someone has to deliver the letters for Mingshu,

7
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,360
I,

8
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,880
as his father, am more suitable.

9
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:24,960
It's not the place for an outsider like you to go.

10
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:25,640
Dad,

11
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,130
your leg is injured.

12
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:29,400
How can you cross the sea to deliver letters?

13
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,640
If anyone goes, it should be me.

14
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,320
I am also a courier for the agency.

15
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,650
Alright, stop arguing.

16
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,280
I'll go.

17
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:35,840
I will come back immediately.

18
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,039
Then I'll go with you.

19
00:01:37,759 --> 00:01:38,560
Wangshu.

20
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:41,080
You can't come with me this time.

21
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:42,840
Why not?

22
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:44,920
You know,

23
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,530
the situation in Malaya is very critical now.

24
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,360
If you go,

25
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,250
I can't guarantee your safety.

26
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:52,160
And I will be distracted.

27
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,960
Our compatriots are in trouble.

28
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,000
I have to go.

29
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,000
You stay here.

30
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,770
Take good care of Dad

31
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,440
and sister-in-law.

32
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,000
Okay?

33
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,040
No.

34
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,280
You want me to watch you

35
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,120
go take risks?

36
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,419
Brother is never coming back.

37
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,090
Now you are leaving too.

38
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:13,920
Wangshu.

39
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,640
Jiadong.

40
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,640
Don't you want to think about it carefully?

41
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,570
If anything happens to you,

42
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:23,370
how can I explain it to Grandma?

43
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,050
Sister-in-law.

44
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,360
The overseas Chinese in Malaya

45
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:27,890
and those

46
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,320
like Mr. Qin who helped us

47
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,810
also have families.

48
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:33,210
When the country is in trouble,

49
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,100
we can't just think of ourselves.

50
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,840
I'll go check on Wangshu.

51
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,560
Jiadong.

52
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:42,280
These damn Japanese!

53
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,650
A perfectly good family

54
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,480
is about to be torn apart by them.

55
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,120
Wangshu.

56
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:17,760
I'm sorry.

57
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:25,560
I know.

58
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,660
Mingshu just passed away,

59
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,380
and now I have to leave.

60
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,840
It makes you sad.

61
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,520
But the invaders are running rampant now.

62
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,850
Our country is in chaos.

63
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,440
We have no choice.

64
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,280
Wangshu.

65
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,079
Actually, there's another reason

66
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,280
why I want you to stay.

67
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:51,079
The whole of Fujian is not peaceful now.

68
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,040
We could run into gunfire at any time.

69
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:53,800
If you stay,

70
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,960
you can at least protect Dad and Sister-in-law.

71
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:58,040
I'll come back as soon as I deliver the Qiaopi.

72
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:58,680
Okay?

73
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:05,240
I'm not stopping you from saving our compatriots.

74
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,490
I'm just worried about you.

75
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,480
I want to go with you.

76
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,320
Can't I?

77
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,080
Wangshu.

78
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,780
We are married now.

79
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,079
We bear the responsibility of two families.

80
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:16,839
If you stay,

81
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,500
I'll feel more at ease.

82
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,200
Mingshu just left us.

83
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,079
If you stay by their side,

84
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,020
Dad will feel a little better,

85
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,800
and Sister-in-law will feel more at ease.

86
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,860
Do you understand?

87
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,280
But I just...

88
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,640
I'm afraid you won't come back

89
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,840
like my brother.

90
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,400
I won't.

91
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,400
I, Chen Jiadong, swear to you,

92
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,400
that I will definitely return

93
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,320
safely and alive.

94
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:44,320
I'll report to you at any time, okay?

95
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,090
Sacred Tree,

96
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,600
please bless my Jiadong

97
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,800
to complete his mission successfully

98
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,860
and return safely.

99
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,040
Please bless my Wangshu,

100
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,440
Dad, and sister-in-law.

101
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,680
Keep them all safe

102
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,460
and grant them a long life.

103
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,040
Also bless our compatriots

104
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,440
to be free from the suffering of war.

105
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,360
May China expel foreign enemies soon

106
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,360
and restore peace and tranquility.

107
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,240
Also bless Jiadong's and my child

108
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,360
to be born safely

109
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,680
and see his father at birth.

110
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,800
Wangshu.

111
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,570
What did you say?

112
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,090
We are having a baby?

113
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,800
Yes, you are going to be a father.

114
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,330
So you must not let anything happen to you.

115
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,880
Okay, put me down.

116
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,210
I'm going to be a father!

117
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,850
I'm going to be a father!

118
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,120
Grandma.

119
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,770
I'm going to be a father!

120
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:50,760
Wangshu.

121
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,080
I promise you.

122
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,440
I promise you and the baby

123
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,159
that I will be safe

124
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,650
and come back alive.

125
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,900
You have to keep your word.

126
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,080
Jiadong,

127
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,400
you must keep your word

128
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,800
and come back safely.

129
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:28,180
We are all waiting for you at home.

130
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:28,960
Okay.

131
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,360
Jiadong.

132
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:36,520
Jiadong.

133
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,540
Brother Liang.

134
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,090
The Japanese

135
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,920
just bombed the Quanzhou dock.

136
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,780
He will take you

137
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,860
away from here via the small pier.

138
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,730
Don't worry.

139
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,290
Wangshu,

140
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,400
I will bring her

141
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,240
back safely.

142
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:51,360
Liang, is Quanzhou still safe?

143
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,320
Quanzhou is

144
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,610
safe for now.

145
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:56,800
I will take good care of your family.

146
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,840
The Qiaopi is of great importance.

147
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:58,600
Leave now.

148
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,120
Hurry.

149
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,320
Come back safely.

150
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,040
Go.

151
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:11,640
Jiadong,

152
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,600
you must come back safely.

153
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,360
Jiadong,

154
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,920
why did you come back?

155
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,920
Mr. Qin, I came back this time

156
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,800
on behalf of Brother Mingshu

157
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,930
to deliver an important Qiaopi to you.

158
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,170
You came back alone?

159
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,570
What about Mingshu?

160
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,240
Didn't he come back with you?

161
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,800
Brother Mingshu...

162
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,580
What happened?

163
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:44,000
When we were leaving,

164
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,780
he was killed by the Japanese.

165
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,240
Those bastards!

166
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,960
We must avenge Mingshu.

167
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,120
Mr. Qin,

168
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:01,170
this Qiaopi is very urgent.

169
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,360
The organization in Quanzhou

170
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,360
told me to hand it to you personally.

171
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,800
According to reliable sources,

172
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,120
the Japanese army plans to

173
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,320
between November and December,

174
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,980
launch an invasion of Malaya.

175
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,080
Please advise all

176
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:16,120
patriotic overseas Chinese organizations and individuals

177
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,240
in Malaya to protect

178
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,570
their personal safety.

179
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:21,040
If in danger, return to China immediately.

180
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:23,200
We will provide assistance.

181
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,500
This is no trivial matter.

182
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,200
I will immediately contact

183
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,360
the organization in Malaya

184
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,690
and hand it over to them.

185
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,039
Along the way,

186
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,880
you must have suffered a lot.

187
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,720
When I left,

188
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,090
the Japanese bombed Quanzhou.

189
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,559
I hope Wangshu and the others

190
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,799
are safe in Kuixia.

191
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:03,640
Mr. Li,

192
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:04,760
please.

193
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:06,330
Jiadong,

194
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:07,240
come here.

195
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:08,880
Let me introduce you.

196
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,120
This is the head of

197
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,560
the Malayan Resistance Organization,

198
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,490
Mr. Li Mingyuan.

199
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,720
Hello, Brother Mingyuan.

200
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,050
My name is Chen Jiadong.

201
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,450
Hello, Jiadong.

202
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,240
We are deeply saddened

203
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,640
by Mingshu's sacrifice.

204
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,360
But I didn't expect

205
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,280
you to take his place

206
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,160
and deliver such

207
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,620
important intelligence.

208
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,320
I thank you on behalf of the organization.

209
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,080
Brother Mingyuan,

210
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,960
you're too kind.

211
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,360
I am duty-bound to finish

212
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,650
what Brother Mingshu entrusted to me.

213
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,040
Please, take a seat.

214
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:35,800
Okay. Please take a seat.

215
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,480
Okay.

216
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:38,280
Here.

217
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,040
Thank you.

218
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,840
Have a seat.

219
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,840
According to this intelligence,

220
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,400
our resistance organization

221
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:51,330
has completely gone underground.

222
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,080
As for those

223
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,440
patriotic overseas Chinese blacklisted by the Japanese,

224
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,400
we will arrange ships as soon as possible

225
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:58,800
to get them out of Malaya.

226
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,360
That's great.

227
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,760
I finally did a good deed

228
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:02,960
for Brother Mingshu.

229
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:03,800
Jiadong.

230
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:05,560
Mr. Qin,

231
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,090
I came here this time

232
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,840
because there is another matter

233
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,300
I hope you can help me with.

234
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:12,000
You don't have to be polite, Mr. Li.

235
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,600
I will definitely do my best.

236
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,800
Well,

237
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,360
in this intelligence,

238
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,440
there is a very important task

239
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,360
that we need to complete.

240
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:19,960
What task?

241
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,120
The current situation of the war of resistance in China

242
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,920
is very grim.

243
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:25,680
The frontline troops

244
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:26,760
need a large amount of medicine

245
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,960
to treat the wounded.

246
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,400
They hope we can, as soon as possible in Malaya,

247
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:31,600
purchase a batch of penicillin

248
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,000
and send it back to China.

249
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,920
But we don't have the ability

250
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,250
to buy so much medicine.

251
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,640
Mr. Qin,

252
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,680
could you perhaps go through the chamber of commerce

253
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:41,480
to help us figure something out?

254
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:42,600
For the war of resistance,

255
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,680
I am bound by duty.

256
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,560
I will definitely find a way.

257
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,560
Thank you.
